ets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c48a752e11ffe3fd7b9aca4b56e2b09ec42b9a","tid":512012,"uid":72173,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:07:21.000Z","msg":"明明每個月賺既錢夠換電話，換電腦<br />\n又夠去旅行<br />\n<br />\n如果唔玩股，日日食放題都得<br />\n點解我咁撚折墮仲用緊部老爺機"},{"pid":"541002fd728343dbc9d9fbb10a9706c97c1236f8","tid":512012,"uid":9506,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:10:54.000Z","msg":"消費＝錢一定變少／一定蝕<br />\n投資＝有機會羸輸<br />\n<br />\n買嘢買貴咗，本身都蝕錢，仲要蝕多啲畀你個奸商？<br />\n投資輸咗錢，本身有風險，正常過正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d78c10d751d9dff0a38c5d4c3a0765139381e60","tid":512012,"uid":133322,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T09:28:27.000Z","msg":"反而我蝕錢先會消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n賺緊果陣就真係唔想洗咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  想儲住舊錢<br />\n<br />\n有次單日輸左本金10%  即刻去買部新電話用<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce6cead2670b394db75075cdb670ac39b784484","tid":512012,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T09:31:46.000Z","msg":"消費d錢就肯定少左<br />\n<br />\n股票有得坐艇坐返家鄉"},{"pid":"b3a4d05978eb0adeccec54f7d5c859d2db33f34a","tid":512012,"uid":47776,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T09:51:41.000Z","msg":"參考下點解賭場要你用籌碼多過用真錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為心理學上人嘅潛意識由細都大都係接觸緊錢<br />\n<br />\n明白錢嘅用途同重要性<br />\n<br />\n相反籌碼嘅認知同潛意識比較細<br />\n<br />\n好多時你都只係會當佢一個片野<br />\n<br />\n你唔會即刻意識到果片野係值一千蚊"},{"pid":"7b01c7dbc0cac727e763661981612aa812d4ee37","tid":512012,"uid":126220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3a4d05978eb0adeccec54f7d5c859d2db33f34a","tid":512012,"uid":47776,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T09:51:41.000Z","msg":"參考下點解賭場要你用籌碼多過用真錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為心理學上人嘅潛意識由細都大都係接觸緊錢<br />\n<br />\n明白錢嘅用途同重要性<br />\n<br />\n相反籌碼嘅認知同潛意識比較細<br />\n<br />\n好多時你都只係會當佢一個片野<br />\n<br />\n你唔會即刻意識到果片野係值一千蚊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T10:04:03.000Z","msg":"所以而家先力推電子貨幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d70f327e6203f4f36437264b11a9f19b3fa0abb","tid":512012,"uid":8246,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T10:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>參考下點解賭場要你用籌碼多過用真錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為心理學上人嘅潛意識由細都大都係接觸緊錢<br />\n<br />\n明白錢嘅用途同重要性<br />\n<br />\n相反籌碼嘅認知同潛意識比較細<br />\n<br />\n好多時你都只係會當佢一個片野<br />\n<br />\n你唔會即刻意識到果片野係值一千蚊</blockquote><br />\n只係覺得數字上既變化，唔同一張張銀紙"},{"pid":"a6097924fb0407414d3264d8ba27681858be52f3","tid":512012,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T10:38:25.000Z","msg":"無啦啦做乜講我<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：今年賺既錢已經洗晒"},{"pid":"24eb4674f34da94164f1b16cd1275245e312c39b","tid":512012,"uid":46642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T16:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75acb3ae79ad058a378265c662fc0d21a4810c25","tid":512012,"uid":16862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T05:32:02.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要之前慳到舊錢，玩左幾個月輸左三分一<br />\n申利好肉赤"},{"pid":"8ce0fa5ba3c7cfc2a752f4c1d7efe2877ebbce19","tid":512012,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T05:37:32.000Z","msg":"以為係戒賭po<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb52d85e0253a9ea290494fd61330439979d0bdf","tid":512012,"uid":7242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T05:39:46.000Z","msg":"Anchoring"},{"pid":"208bc9a655a1c3951356f06d63d98328137a